        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3240218982" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer745598530788081264">It&apos;s Borges: if you get it, you love it, if you don&apos;t, oh well, if you&apos;re not sure, you shouldn&apos;t start with this at all, but with the more inescapable Fictions + The Aleph.<br/><br/>Also you can be mean to HP all you want, Jorge, but you still wrote a piece of fan fiction for him! Ha-ha, you like Lovecraft!</span>
  <span id="freeText745598530788081264" style="display:none">It's Borges: if you get it, you love it, if you don't, oh well, if you're not sure, you shouldn't start with this at all, but with the more inescapable Fictions + The Aleph.<br /><br />Also you can be mean to HP all you want, Jorge, but you still wrote a piece of fan fiction for him! Ha-ha, you like Lovecraft!</span>
