  <span id="freeText1447867773851068992" style="display:none">102nd book for 2018.<br /><br />These stories just didn't click for me. I found neither the characters nor the ideas particularly interesting. I'd be willing to try one of his more famous collections at some later point, but this first exposure to Borges left me cold. <br /><br />Perhaps I should wait until my Spanish is sufficiently improved that I can tackle him in the original.<br /><br />2-stars.</span>
